"{\"uid\": \"standard.co.uk-news-world-paris-olympics-2024-swim-poo-river-seine-protest-b1166240.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"To use the search feature, we need your consent to load Google Custom Search, which may use cookies or similar technologies.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 56, \"end\": 76, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google Custom Search\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please click 'Allow and Continue' below to enable search.\", \"from\": 125, \"to\": 182, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"See our privacy policy for more information.\", \"from\": 183, \"to\": 227, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"News|World  Furious Frenchmen are threatening to turn the Seine into a sewer this Sunday in a bizarre protest against the eye-watering costs of Olympic preparations.\", \"from\": 229, \"to\": 394, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 287, \"end\": 292, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999999995407052, \"rank\": 3.721715955965523e-10, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The movement, cheekily dubbed #JeChieDansLaSeineLe23Juin (I will poo in the Seine on June 23), has gained traction after Paris MayorAnne Hidalgoboasted she'd take a dip to prove the river's cleanliness.\", \"from\": 396, \"to\": 598, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 472, \"end\": 477, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999999995407052, \"rank\": 3.721715955965523e-10, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}, {\"begin\": 517, \"end\": 522, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.0517964363751745e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hidalgo, however, has now back-pedalled on her pledge, conveniently citing the hastily-called French elections as reason to postpone her plunge.\", \"from\": 600, \"to\": 744, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 694, \"end\": 710, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1951_French_legislative_election\", \"score\": 0.7329045276262378, \"rank\": 0.36431615795199573, \"text\": \"French elections\", \"types\": [\"Q40231\", \"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1951_French_legislative_election\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1951_French_legislative_election\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A staggering \\u00a31.2 billion has been poured into purifying the Seine for Olympic swimmers and triathletes, as the river prepares to host key events during the Games.\", \"from\": 746, \"to\": 909, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 807, \"end\": 812, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999999995407052, \"rank\": 3.721715955965523e-10, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A spokesman for the movement told news outlet Actu Paris: \\\"The problem is that all the resources that have been invested have not been to resolve all the social problems we have.\", \"from\": 911, \"to\": 1089, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 962, \"end\": 967, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.0517964363751745e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have 